headline: UGG Opens ‘Feel House’ in Los Angeles, a Multi-Sensory Retail Concept Co-Curated by Post Malone
summary: LOS ANGELES, November 20, 2024--Launched in April 2022 by Southern California-based brand UGG® (a division of Deckers Brands [NYSE: DECK]), Feel House returns once again as a multi-sensory retail experience dedicated to making self-expression comfortable for all. headline: Nordstrom Expands Footprint by Opening Store in Florida's Lakeland
summary: JWN plans to expand its presence in Florida with a new Rack store in the Lakeside Village, offering a varied collection of high-quality brands at reasonable prices.

headline: TJX Beats Q3 Earnings & Sales Estimates, Raises '25 EPS & Margin View
summary: TJX's Q3 results reflect higher earnings and sales amid an increase in customer transactions. Management raises its profit outlook for fiscal 2025.
